                    <section class="o_colored_level pb8">
                        <h3 data-anchor="true" id="table_of_content_heading_1688393039779_116"><i class="fa fa-info-circle mr-3" aria-hidden="true"></i>About Sakaya.co</h3>
                    </section>
                    <section class="s_faq_collapse pb40 o_colored_level s_faq_collapse_boxed" data-snippet="s_faq_collapse" data-name="Accordion">
                        <div class="container">
                        <div id="myCollapse1681439039965" class="accordion" role="tablist">

                            <div class="card" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon collapsed" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439039966">What is Sakaya.co</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439039965" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439039966">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p class="card-text">Sakaya.co was created with the hope of being the most informative and professional Japanese sake marketplace globally! The idea behind Sakaya.co is a stubborn desire to find ways to get the freshest and most accurate expression of sake in the hands of discerning customers the world over.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439039967">What is our product offering?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439039965" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439039967">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p class="card-text">We sell Sake, Shochu, Umeshu, Fruit Liqueur, Awamori, Japanese Whisky and Japanese Wine.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="card-header collapsed s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439039968">What are our operating hours?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439039965" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439039968">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">We are an online marketplace so we’re open for business 24/7/365!</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="card-header collapsed s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439039969">What are our accepted payment methods?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439039965" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439039969">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">We accept credit cards via Stripe. Accepted credit cards include:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>American Express</li>
                                    <li>China UnionPay (CUP)</li>
                                    <li>Discover &amp; Diners</li>
                                    <li>Japan Credit Bureau (JCB)</li>
                                    <li>Mastercard</li>
                                    <li>Visa</li>
                                </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="o_colored_level pb8">
                        <h3 data-anchor="true" id="table_of_content_heading_1688393039779_117"><i class="fa fa-plane mr-3" aria-hidden="true"></i>Sake dropshipping</h3>
                    </section>
                    <section class="s_faq_collapse pb40 o_colored_level s_faq_collapse_boxed" data-snippet="s_faq_collapse" data-name="Accordion">
                        <div class="container">
                        <div id="myCollapse1681439071835" class="accordion" role="tablist">

                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon collapsed" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439071836">What types of Japanese sake are available for dropshipping?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439071835" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439071836">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">The platform may offer a range of different types of Japanese sake, including junmai, daiginjo, ginjo, and nigori. These different types of sake are made using different processes and ingredients, and can vary in taste and price.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439071837">How is Japanese sake shipped to customers?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439071835" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439071837">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">The supplier would be responsible for shipping the sake to customers, using a reputable courier or postal service. The customer would receive the sake directly from the supplier, without Sakaya.co ever handling the product itself.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439071838">Is there a minimum order quantity for Japanese sake?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439071835" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439071838">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">As we don’t offer free shipping (unless on promotion), there is no MOQ.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="o_colored_level pb8">
                        <h3 data-anchor="true" id="table_of_content_heading_1688393039779_118"><i class="fa fa-truck mr-3" aria-hidden="true"></i>Shipping</h3>
                    </section>
                    <section class="s_faq_collapse pb40 o_colored_level s_faq_collapse_boxed" data-snippet="s_faq_collapse" data-name="Accordion">
                        <div class="container">
                        <div id="myCollapse1681439102713" class="accordion" role="tablist">
                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439102714">When is my order shipped?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439102713" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439102714">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">Once you have placed your order, our system automatically relays the order to our partner sakagura or merchants, and they usually need 1-2 days to process, pick and pack the bottle(s) for safe delivery. When it leaves their warehouse, our system will automatically send you an email with a tracking number (be sure to check your spam/junk/bulk folders as emails sometimes land there.). </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439102713">Can customers track their shipment?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439102713" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439102713">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">Yes, once an order is shipped by the merchant, you will receive an email notification with tracking code if shipping is done via FedEx.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439102715">Do I need to be present to sign for my package?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439102713" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439102715">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">Yes, delivery will require proof of age and signature. Depending on the recipient’s country, most countries require alcohol shipments to be signed for by a person 21 years of age or older. Please make sure the receiver is of legal drinking age in the country of his or her residence.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="o_colored_level pb8">
                        <h3 data-anchor="true" id="table_of_content_heading_1688393039779_119"><i class="fa fa-refresh mr-3" aria-hidden="true"></i>Return / Refund</h3>
                    </section>
                    <section class="s_faq_collapse pb40 o_colored_level s_faq_collapse_boxed" data-snippet="s_faq_collapse" data-name="Accordion">
                        <div class="container">
                        <div id="myCollapse1681439123207" class="accordion" role="tablist">
                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="card-header collapsed s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439123208">Terms of service</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439123207" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439123208">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">We cannot cancel an order once it's been completed. Please be reminded to double check your order before order confirmation and payment. We do not offer any return or refund. However, if you notice that you have received wrong or broken items, please notify us within 24 hours of receiving the goods either by email (hello@sakaya.co) and we will follow up with the courier and sender (merchant). Please remember to quote your order number when contacting support.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439123209">What if I am not satisfied with my order?</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439123207" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439123209">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">AWe encourage you to write to us at hello@sakaya.co and let us know how we can make things better. Whilst we cannot control the quality of the shipment and packaging by our vendors, we will try our very best to accommodate requests that are within reason.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="o_colored_level pb8">
                        <h3 data-anchor="true" id="table_of_content_heading_1688393039779_120"><i class="fa fa-question-circle mr-3" aria-hidden="true"></i>Other Questions</h3>
                    </section>
                    <section class="s_faq_collapse pb40 o_colored_level s_faq_collapse_boxed" data-snippet="s_faq_collapse" data-name="Accordion">
                        <div class="container">
                        <div id="myCollapse1681439123210" class="accordion" role="tablist">
                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon collapsed" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439123211">Representation of Legal Drinking Age</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439123210" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439123211">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">It is illegal to sell alcohol to customers who are not of legal drinking age in their country of residence. It is the customers’ responsibility to ensure their logins are not misused by any person under your country’s respective legal drinking age.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card bg-white" data-name="Item">
                            <a href="#" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed card-header s_faq_collapse_right_icon" data-target="#myCollapseTab1681439123212">Contact</a>
                            <div class="collapse" data-parent="#myCollapse1681439123210" role="tabpanel" id="myCollapseTab1681439123212">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="card-text">If you experience problems regarding a sake purchase, you can contact our support via email at hello@sakaya.co. Please have your order number ready at hand when contacting support.</p>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                    <li>sakaya.co</li>
                                    <li>hello@sakaya.co</li>
                                </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    </div>
